	<string name="choosePieceDesign">It\'s important that you can tell your pieces apart, so make sure you choose the right piece set.
To do that click on the cog wheel or your username(top right corner) and then click on \'piece set\'.</string>
	<string name="promotionZone">When some of your pieces reach or leave the first three ranks in your opponent\'s territory you can choose to promote your piece and make it stronger.</string>
	<string name="senteGoesFirst">In shogi the player who goes first is called sente and the player who goes second is called gote. Sente is sometimes represented by black color and gote by white. Make any move as sente to continue.</string>
	<string name="introComplete">You now know some basics, but this part of tutorial is still under construction. For now learn how individual pieces move.</string>
	<string name="theRook">飛車</string>
	<string name="itMovesInStraightLines">它以直線移動</string>
	<string name="rookIntro">飛車是一個強大的棋子，你準備好來指揮它了嗎？</string>
	<string name="rookGoal">把飛車移到星號格吧!</string>
	<string name="rookPromotion">飛車升變會變成強大的龍王。別忘記您也可以將棋子移出敵陣後同時升變</string>
	<string name="rookSummary">飛車可以前後左右直衝無限格</string>
	<string name="dragonSummary">它的走法跟飛車很像，但更強，因為它也可以任何方向斜走一格</string>
	<string name="grabAllTheStars">吃掉所有的星星！</string>
	<string name="theFewerMoves">The fewer moves you make, the more points you win!</string>
	<string name="rookComplete">恭喜！你已經懂得如何使用飛車了。</string>
	<string name="theBishop">角行</string>
	<string name="itMovesDiagonally">它以斜線移動</string>
	<string name="bishopIntro">接下來我們來學如何控制角行的移動。</string>
	<string name="bishopPromotion">角行升變之後會變得更強，它會變成{龍馬}</string>
	<string name="bishopSummary">角行可以任何方向斜走無限格</string>
	<string name="horseSummary">龍馬也可以斜衝，但它也可以前後左右走一格</string>
	<string name="bishopComplete">恭喜！你現在知道如何掌握你的主教了。</string>
	<string name="theKing">王將</string>
	<string name="theMostImportantPiece">最重要的棋子</string>
	<string name="kingIntro">你就是國王。如果你輸了這場戰鬥，你就輸了這一局棋賽。</string>
	<string name="theKingIsSlow">王將走得比較慢</string>
	<string name="kingSummary">王將可以行走任何方向，但只能走一格</string>
	<string name="kingComplete">現在連國王都要聽令於你了！</string>
	<string name="theKnight">騎士</string>
	<string name="itMovesInAnLShape">它以L字形行走，但只能前進!</string>
	<string name="knightIntro">給你一個小挑戰，桂馬是一個．．．比較特別的棋子。</string>
	<string name="knightsHaveAFancyWay">桂馬有著特別酷的跳法!</string>
	<string name="knightsCanJumpOverObstacles">桂馬可以跳過任何棋子!</string>
	<string name="knightSummary">桂馬可以以L字形向前跳躍，但只能向前兩格並左或右一格。桂馬的走法不受其他棋子限制，因為它可以從它們頭上跳過去</string>
	<string name="pknightSummary">Promoted knight moves are completely different from the unpromoted knight, but you can notice it moves the same as the gold general, so make sure to study that one thoroughly.</string>
	<string name="knightPromotion">桂馬也可以升變，但它的走法變得完全不同，請特別留意</string>
	<string name="knightComplete">恭喜！你現在已經精通了騎士的用法。</string>
	<string name="thePawn">士兵</string>
	<string name="itMovesForwardOnly">向前邁進!</string>
	<string name="pawnIntro">士兵也許弱小，但它們的潛能比你想的還多。</string>
	<string name="pawnsMoveOneSquareOnly">步兵可以向前方走一格，吃子方法也一樣</string>
	<string name="pawnPromotion">步兵也可以升變，而走法也當然，跟金將一模一樣</string>
	<string name="pawnComplete">恭喜！士兵對你來說已經毫無秘密可言了。</string>
	<string name="pawnSummary">步兵走法單純，很好理解</string>
	<string name="tokinSummary">You should already be familiar with this pattern by now.</string>
	<string name="theLance">香車</string>
	<string name="itMovesStraightForward">它只能向前衝</string>
	<string name="lanceIntro">小心使用</string>
	<string name="lancesAreStraighforward">它可以向前衝無限格，很簡單對吧?</string>
	<string name="lancePromotion">香車升變之後，走法完全不同。沒錯，走法跟金將一樣</string>
	<string name="lanceSummary">向前衝，有夠簡單的啦</string>
	<string name="planceSummary">跟金將一樣</string>
	<string name="lanceComplete">太棒了！</string>
	<string name="theGold">金將</string>
